videos.headline: Case expresses key to the Rebels' win over Gamecocks
videos.description: Win Case discusses how Ole Miss answered the call to secure the victory over South Carolina, 67-61.

videos.headline: Rebels open SEC tourney with gritty win vs. Gamecocks
videos.description: Amaree Abram comes in big off the bench, scoring 20 to power 13-seed Ole Miss past 12-seed South Carolina, 67-61, to advance to the second round of the SEC tourney.
